<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٥٠ - <span class="c2">(١٣١٨)</span> حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5187">قُتَيْبَةُ بْنُ سَعِيدٍ </a>، حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5361">مَالِكٌ </a>. ح، وَحَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/7021">يَحْيَى بْنُ يَحْيَى </a>وَاللَّفْظُ لَهُ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> قَرَأْتُ عَلَى <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5361">مَالِكٍ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5914">أَبِي الزُّبَيْرِ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1091">جَابِرِ بْنِ عَبْدِ اللهِ </a>قَالَ: <span class="c2">« نَحَرْنَا مَعَ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٨٨⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>رَسُولِ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> عَامَ الْحُدَيْبِيَةِ الْبَدَنَةَ عَنْ سَبْعَةٍ وَالْبَقَرَةَ عَنْ سَبْعَةٍ ».<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>